high_descs: take the tomato from the fridge
take the tomato to the microwave
cook the tomato in the microwave then remove
take the cooked tomato to the fridge
put the tomato in the fridge
anns.task_desc: cook a tomato in the microwave then place it in the fridge

high_descs: Turn around to face the fridge.
Grab the tomato inside the fridge.
With the tomato, turn left and walk to the microwave to the right.
Place the tomato inside the microwave, cook it, then remove it.
With the cooked tomato, walk to the fridge to your right.
Place the cooked tomato inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked tomato inside the fridge.

high_descs: Turn round and go to the refrigerator across from you.
Pull out the tomato on the second shelf, to the right of the green cup.
Turn to your left and walk towards the sink until you reach the microwave on your right, just past the refrigerator.
Place the tomato in the microwave, heat it up, then remove the tomato from the microwave.
Turn to your right and go back to the refrigerator on your left.
Place the tomato back in the refrigerator, in the middle of the second shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm tomato in the reffrigerator.
